This widely-distributed species (
<bibRefCitation id="EFD34B4CFFD7FFCBFD32773C301BFEEE" author="De Ridder, M. &amp; Segers, H." box="[717,1028,295,320]" pageId="9" pagination="1 - 481" refId="ref4028" refString="De Ridder, M. &amp; Segers, H. (1997) Monogonont Rotifera recorded in the World literature (except Africa) from 1960 - 1992. Studiedocumenten van het K. B. I. N., 88, 1 - 481." type="journal article" year="1997">De Ridder &amp; Segers, 1997</bibRefCitation>
